# RAG corpora live here: the Wikipedia dumps (*.xml.bz2) and the FTS5 indexes
# (*.db) built from them by `python -m ayre_rag ingest`. All of it is large,
# generated/downloaded, and consume-only — none of it belongs in git (see
# Distribution_Contents.md "never-in-repo"). Ignore everything in this folder
# except this file, which keeps the folder present in the repo so a fresh clone
# has an obvious, in-tree home to build indexes into (config/rag.json defaults
# index_db_path here). Mirrors the models/.gitignore pattern for bin/, python/, models/.
*
!.gitignore
